Stella Mwangi has bagged a massive score on TV's most watched show, Being Mary Jane. The series stars Gabrielle Union in the lead role of Mary Jane Paul, a successful cable news anchor who has a closet packed with designer clothes and shoes, a beautiful home, a nice car, and the drive to achieve even greater heights. Yet something is missing. A favourite among many Kenyan women.It is confirmed that Stella's single, Set It Off, will feature as a soundtrack on the third episode of BET Africa&rsquo;s show, Being Mary Jane Season 4 set to air on January 24, 2017 (for the US audience). The multi-talented Kenyan - Norwegian artiste has been making Hollywood headlines with her EP since its release in 2016.